    "course_title": "CLINICAL OPHTHALMOLOGY ROTATION",
    "description": "Provides experience in ocular examination, problem solving skills, and formulation of diagnostic and therapeutic plans for animals presenting with eye disease. Ocular examination as part of the complete physical examination and ocular manifestations of systemic diseases are emphasized.",
